IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User sebastian.pleschko@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.mailpass.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox
AltMap no
Flatten .


Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail" !"[Gmail]/Important"
Create Both
SyncState *
Remove Both


